# Accessible Modals ü™ü

Create fully accessible modal dialogs.

## Structure:
```html
<div 
    role="dialog" 
    aria-modal="true"
    aria-labelledby="dialog-title"
>
    <h2 id="dialog-title">Confirm Delete</h2>
    <p>Are you sure?</p>
    <button>Cancel</button>
    <button>Delete</button>
</div>
```

## Requirements:
1. **Focus trap** - Keep focus inside
2. **Escape to close** - Close on Escape key
3. **Return focus** - Focus trigger on close
4. **Background inert** - Disable background

## JavaScript:
```javascript
function openModal(modal, trigger) {
    modal.hidden = false;
    modal.querySelector('button').focus();

    // Trap focus
    modal.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
        if (e.key === 'Escape') {
            closeModal(modal, trigger);
        }
    });
}

function closeModal(modal, trigger) {
    modal.hidden = true;
    trigger.focus(); // Return focus
}
```
